      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WALKING CARPET (6) goes very well this trip starting 11 times for five wins and four minors. Hit the frame latest (20.00) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Rates on top and should go close. NOBBY (8) scored two back in one of the fastest times on the card then was always well back and could manage only a 6 length 7th at this track (20.19) latest. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Worth following up. GRAB A DONUT (4) ran below best last time finishing fifth (20.12) over 366m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Should be in this for a long way. HOOKED ON MAGIC (3) is likely to have admirers.",
